<plot>Charley Barnet and his Orchestra provide the music, while the King Sisters (Alyce, Donna, Louise and Yvonne), Romo Vincent and the Sportsmen Quartet handle the sings on such numbers as "You Belong to My Heart" - "Lullaby of Birland" - "Easy Street", and "Once Upon Your Heart", while Barnet's band also tosses in "Redskin Rhumba," "Shadrack" and other tunes. This Universal Featurette carried 2006 as its in-house production number.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?083131</url></doc>
